lous party!<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><strong>Activities -&nbsp;<\/strong>Mitzvah Merchandise provides a wide variety of activities available for rent. From games like ping pong and basketball, Mitzvah Merchandise has the entertainment sector of the party covered. In addition to the numerous games we provide, we have other activities that suit people of all ages.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Dancing -&nbsp;<\/strong>Mitzvah Merchandise&rsquo; exceptional DJ service ensures the party is enjoyed by all. All of the playlists\/songs are based on the child&rsquo;s requests, and our DJs know how to set the mood. We have full stereo and audio equipment for defining volume and a variety of sound effects that animate the party. Our equipment include advanced mixers, CD decks to DJ controllers, audio interfaces<\/p>","align":"left"}}},"block_order":["1582424609762-0","1582424609762-1"],"settings":{}},"1582424673450":{"type":"columns","blocks":{"1582424673450-0":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"title":"Aminah Mitchell -","text":"<p>\"My experience with Mitzvah Merchandise was exceptional and no hassle. I thought the procedure would be laborious, but it was the opposite! Our daughter loved all the activities and games that were orchestrated by the staff of Mitzvah Merchandise. Mitzvah Merchandise facilitated and streamlined the process of the party and was really flexible; for that I say Mazel Tov!\"<\/p>","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/chris-weinberg-events-luxury-miami-event-planner-10.jpg","image_align":"top center"}},"1582424673450-1":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"title":"Hugh Fulton -","text":"<p>\"Mitzvah Merchandise was just the thing I needed for my duaghter&rsquo;s Bat Mitzvah, and it was perfect! The staff was very responsive and professional, the delivery\/setup\/breakdown was done in a timely and organized manner, and all of their products on the website are lovely and good quality. Highly recommend it to anyone!\"<\/p>","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ae3f72d9741673ad6b370ce42e56d2e9.jpg","image_align":"top center"}},"1582424673450-2":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"title":"Richard Lehmann -","text":"<p>\"I rented from Mitzvah Merchandise for my son&rsquo;s Bar Mitzvah, and I was pleased! The website had various astonishing options and price points that suited the party. Within a short amount of time, everything was prepared, and my son was jubilated. I undoubtedly recommend Mitzvah Merchandise!\"<\/p>","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Mitzvah-Celebration-Anthonys-Pier-9-26.jpg","image_align":"top center"}}},"block_order":["1582424673450-0","1582424673450-1","1582424673450-2"],"settings":{"title":"Satisfied Customers!"}},"collection-filters":{"type":"collection-filters","settings":{"product_tags_enable":true,"product_sorting_enable":true}},"product-template":{"type":"product-template","settings":{"enable_ajax":true,"stock_enable":false,"enable_payment_button":false,"social_sharing_products":true}},"product-recommendations":{"type":"product-recommendations","settings":{"show_product_recommendations":true,"heading":"You may also like"}},"featured-products-subsection":{"type":"featured-products-subsection","settings":{"collection":""}},"cart-template":{"type":"cart-template","settings":{"cart_notes_enable":true}}},"content_for_index":["slideshow","featured-collections","image-content","1582423999577","1582424609762","1582424673450"]},"presets":{"Snowboards":{"checkout_accent_color":"#006eff","checkout_banner_background_color":"#fff","checkout_button_color":"#006eff","checkout_call_to_action_color":"#006eff","checkout_use_header_image":false,"color_body_bg":"#f7f7f7","color_body_headings":"#030303","color_body_text":"#666","color_button_bg":"#006eff","color_button_text":"#fff","color_content_bg":"#fff","color_footer_bg":"#030303","color_footer_text":"#fff","color_header_bg":"#030303","color_header_links":"#fff","color_hero_bg":"#006eff","color_hero_text":"#fff","color_newsletter_input":"#1a1a1a","type_accent_family":"unica_one_n4